if it is to grant independence to namibia angola has said it would 
take three to four years to send the cubans home 
the talks among south africa cuba and angola on ending the 
13year angolan civil war and granting independence to namibia 
began wednesday 
the negotiators also discussed south africas support for the 
antimarxist guerrillas fighting angolas government said sources 
close to the south african delegation who spoke on condition of 
anonymity 
