liedetector test and agreed because she had nothing to hide 
i took the test and i failed it she told ksltv 
she said that when cuts continued to surface in some orings 
she was moved to a filing job and asked to resign 
dockstader said no employees were fired because of the 
investigations but wouldnt say whether any were disciplined 
he said security at hydrapaks plant was strict including 
employee badges for admission and escorts for visitors 
but crocker said security was lax and that anyone could walk 
into the plant 
