the extensive modification of the b1 aspin said and added in 
fact the gao had training reports that cited spare parts shortages 
as the primary cause of the training limitation 
once again the facts seem to contradict pentagon assertions 
about the b1 aspin said 
shortages of b1 bombers ready to fly affect not only training 
but plans for placing bombers on alert to respond to a nuclear 
attack on the united states 
alert status is the bombers reason for being aspin said 
if thats adversely affected and it is here then youve got 
problems 
