conjunction with the socalled stealth b2 bomber as the b52 
replacement in the nations arsenal of strategic weapons the b2 
nicknamed for its capability to evade enemy air defenses will have 
its first public flight in november 
the last b1 was delivered on april 30 the air force said the 
total cost of the program was 273 billion but that figure 
doesnt include any improvements 
