pensacola naval air station and hold his head under water 
the sailor airman recruit lee mirecki 19 of appleton wis 
died in the incident march 2 
i never authorized a person to be placed back in the pool 
said cmdr allan p nesbitt iii torchias predecessor that is 
something that would not occur and did not occur 
but he also said that regulations at the time did allow 
instructors to pull tired students away from the walls of the pool 
