order has deteriorated since maung maung lifted martial law 
wednesday 
security in the city isnt so good especially after the 
darkness comes on said an asian diplomat the streets are 
nearly empty at night theft and looting cases are reported 
incessantly 
the government has been silent on the most recent protests and 
on the stream of demands from prominent figures for immediate 
democracy that silence along with deterioriating social conditions 
has provoked rumors that ne win and other officials may be 
preparing to flee burma 
